text.tspan: Number of world citizens living under different political regimes
The Polity IV score captures the type of political regime for each country on a range from -10 (full autocracy) to +10
(full democracy). Regimes that fall into the middle of this spectrum are called anocracies.
Source: World Population by Political Regime they live in (OWID (2016))
